                "El **evidence bundle** final: arquitectura, READMEs, system/model cards, licencia, video "
                "y defensa técnica de trade-offs. Cada artefacto es localizable (path/hash) como exige CF-5. "
                "La defensa nombra límites y no-go, no solo logros.",
                "Mecanismo: required artifacts presentes, license != '', defense_notes con tradeoffs y "
                "limitations, paths localizables. Bundle incompleto bloquea master.",
                "Contrato. Entrada: checklist de artefactos + defensa. Salida: evidence bundle completo y "
                "verificable. Error: falta artefacto → `BLOCK_INCOMPLETE_PORTFOLIO`. Defensa vacía → "
                "`PREPARE_TECHNICAL_DEFENSE`.",
                f"Aplicación `{case}-4B`: arch/README/cards/license/video + defense con trade-offs.",
            ],
            "arquitectura_readme_cards_defensa.py",
            textwrap.dedent(
                """\
                def portfolio_ok(rec):
                    need = {
                        "architecture",
                        "readme",
                        "system_card",
                        "license",
                        "video",
                        "defense",
                    }
                    return (
                        need <= set(rec["artifacts"])
                        and bool(rec["license"])
                        and "tradeoffs" in rec["defense"]
                        and "limitations" in rec["defense"]
                        and all(rec["paths"].values())
                    )

                rec = {
                    "artifacts": [
                        "architecture",
                        "readme",
                        "system_card",
                        "license",
                        "video",
                        "defense",
                    ],
                    "license": "MIT-synthetic",
                    "defense": {
                        "tradeoffs": "latency vs deep retrieval",
                        "limitations": "synthetic benchmark only",
                    },
                    "paths": {
                        "architecture": "docs/arch.md",
                        "system_card": "cards/system.md",
                    },
                }
                print("ok", portfolio_ok(rec))
                print("artifacts", len(rec["artifacts"]))
                print("license", rec["license"])
                """
            ),
            "Cierre de S52-T4-B: conserva evidence bundle completo y verificable, la evidencia de `BLOCK_INCOMPLETE_PORTFOLIO` y la ruta humana `PREPARE_TECHNICAL_DEFENSE`.",
            "Demo: bloquea portafolio sin system card",
            "demo_arquitectura_readme_cards_defensa.py",
            textwrap.dedent(
                """\
                arts = {"architecture", "readme", "license", "video", "defense"}
                print("complete", "system_card" in arts)
                print("action", "BLOCK_INCOMPLETE_PORTFOLIO")
                print("defense_tradeoffs", True)
                """
            ),
            "Evidence bundle completo: paths, cards, licencia y defensa con límites.",
            "tip",
            "Contrato local",
        ),
    ]
    return pack_topics(specs)


